methods.registerTimeSource:
Register the time column and index from a new table to replay. Most users will use replay,
 replayGrouped, or replayGroupedLastBy instead of this function.

:param index: (io.deephaven.db.v2.utils.Index) - table index
:param timestampSource: (io.deephaven.db.v2.sources.ColumnSource<io.deephaven.db.tables.utils.DBDateTime>) - column source containing time information.
methods.setTime:
Sets the current replay time.

:param updatedTime: (long) - new replay time.
